Description: A package aiming at researching Bayesian Vector heterogeneous autoregressive process.
    `bvhar` can model VAR, VHAR, Bayesian VAR (BVAR), and Bayesian VHAR (BVHAR).
    It can also generate one Normal-inverse-Wishart matrix for the sake of simulation setting.
